data.description: This 2 bedroom 1 bathroom home might just be that little slice of Northern Michigan you've been searching for. An open concept living space is great for entertaining and a large exterior shed gives the home some extra storage and work space. The home is being sold ''As Is''. Buyer and buyer's agent to verify all information. Showings to begin Monday 2/26/24.
